{"tid":253230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人類最恐怖】住「棺材屋」轉個身都難 真實生活其實係咁","createTime":"2017-05-22T08:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T14:39:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be4acc3a4b4ff245a66d391cc265a57b601b6135","tid":253230,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"2017年03月29日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490692163_0095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490692163_0095.jpg&h=2fb72a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490692162_352e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490692162_352e.jpg&h=5a9933a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國多塞特郡多徹斯特附近一個乳牛養殖場，被揭發虐待乳牛，一隻隻乳牛只能居住在狹窄的「棺材屋」，慘變成擠迫戶，環境極不人道。<br />\n<br />\n從拍攝的照片看到，養殖場內的乳牛住在一個個細小、獨立的「棺材屋」，由於地方太狹小，牛隻想爬回屋內，都要費盡氣力才能成功，部份牛隻也因為居住環境擠迫，導致身體多處擦傷。根據英國法例規定，只有8周及以下的牛隻才能居住在獨立的飼養屋內，但現場所見有些牛隻已經六個月大，明顯違規。<br />\n該養殖場的乳牛長大後，便會被運到英國不同的農場產奶，牠們的奶製品會供應予馬莎等大型超市集團。馬莎發言人表示，對照片感到「失望及完全不能接受」，願意與有關方面合作，立即採取行動糾正問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170329/56490684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170329%2F56490684&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3aa72add\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170329%2F56490684&h=7b2fe63d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170329/56490684</a>"},{"pid":"51c6684791e5c7034d37504efbdf181d83820385","tid":253230,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"望下香港d籠屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係有人住緊嫁"},{"pid":"386d5d7425e77c31cf73e0d04771bb18e344cde8","tid":253230,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32093ff413d85c9e1e7caba0de9368e0f26f26c","tid":253230,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"富裕香港驚現悲慘&quot;棺材房&quot; 房東月賺20萬港幣<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/mobile/kalaok/5361086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Fmobile%2Fkalaok%2F5361086&d=OeNbSnhVY7UVR%2FdNhh%2F7B9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=677b5bc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/mobile/kalaok/5361086</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i163.photobucket.com/albums/t282/airmalau/hk12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi163.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ft282%2Fairmalau%2Fhk12.jpg&h=608156e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"632284e509f3618d62b1e5690b911124b7429dc9","tid":253230,"uid":109151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"香港人連牛也不如"},{"pid":"7f5031cbf0bc002c05a7e05f2fc6e95ce092c37b","tid":253230,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfb9da1187640d8b78820a82c5ada0eea81e333e","tid":253230,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T10:24:54.000Z","msg":"真係好撚痴線"},{"pid":"765ef917484d63c21aae349d1ba28b705b4b87cd","tid":253230,"uid":103544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"真係虧佢地諗得出"},{"pid":"0c8eda6229831f3424102aad8aac0611f149d8d4","tid":253230,"uid":53026,"like":